⊃∩⌟▽⋅⊙∘                                               # select those lines
▽¬×⊃(≥@0|≤@9)⊜⊃⊢□↥↥∩×⊃(≥@A|≤@Z|≥@0|≤@9|=@_)⊸⌵/◇$"_ _" # names in normal lines
⊙⍚(↘+1⊣⊚⊸=@.°$"import _;")                            # imported names
